---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="ダークモード — 地域おこし協力隊DAO">
  <div class="dark">
    <!-- Nav -->
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="nav-logo">
        <div class="nav-logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="9" stroke="#00D4AA" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="3" fill="#00D4AA"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span>協力隊DAO</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#mission">Mission</a>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#join" class="nav-btn">Join DAO</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
          Decentralized Autonomous Organization
        </div>
        <h1>地域の未来を、<br /><span class="gradient-text">分散型</span>で描く。</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">地域おこし協力隊 × DAO。テクノロジーの力で、全国の地域課題に新しい解法を。</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#join" class="btn-primary">コミュニティに参加</a>
          <a href="#mission" class="btn-ghost">詳しく見る →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">47</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Prefectures</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">DAO</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Governance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">Web3</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label">Infrastructure</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section id="mission" class="mission">
      <div class="mission-inner">
        <span class="section-label">Mission</span>
        <h2>地方と都市の境界を溶かし、<br />新しい地域経済圏をつくる。</h2>
        <p>地域おこし協力隊DAOは、全国7,200人以上の協力隊員をWeb3でつなぐ実験的コミュニティ。知恵を共有し、プロジェクトを立ち上げ、DAOのガバナンスで意思決定を行う。従来の「上から下」ではない、フラットな地域づくりのかたち。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section id="features" class="features">
      <div class="features-header">
        <span class="section-label">Features</span>
        <h2>What we offer</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4AA" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>分散型ガバナンス</h3>
          <p>トークンベースの意思決定。コミュニティの方向性を全員で決める、透明性の高い運営モデル。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4AA" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>ナレッジシェアリング</h3>
          <p>移住、活動、資金調達。各地の成功と失敗をオープンに共有し、コミュニティの集合知に。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4AA" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <line x1="19" y1="8" x2="19" y2="14"/>
              <line x1="22" y1="11" x2="16" y2="11"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>クロスリージョン協働</h3>
          <p>地域の壁を越えたプロジェクト立ち上げ。共通課題を持つ隊員同士がDAO上で協働。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00D4AA" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>トークンエコノミー</h3>
          <p>貢献に応じたトークン配布。地域経済を活性化する新しいインセンティブモデル。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section id="join" class="cta">
      <div class="cta-glow"></div>
      <div class="cta-content">
        <span class="section-label">Join the movement</span>
        <h2>地域の未来を、<br />一緒につくろう。</h2>
        <p>地域おこし協力隊の現役隊員、OB/OG、地域に関わりたいすべての方を歓迎します。</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary btn-large">DAOに参加する</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-left">
          <span class="footer-logo">地域おこし協力隊DAO</span>
          <span class="footer-org">Powered by 株式会社あるやうむ</span>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-right">
          <a href="#">Discord</a>
          <a href="#">Twitter</a>
          <a href="#">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← デザイン一覧に戻る</a>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .dark {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    background: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #00D4AA;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* Nav */
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 48px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 28px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: #666;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .nav-btn {
    color: #0a0a0a !important;
    background: #00D4AA;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
    color: #0a0a0a !important;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 48px 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-grid-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #888;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-badge-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #00D4AA;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00D4AA, #00A3FF);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: #00D4AA;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.25);
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 18px 48px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    padding: 14px 0;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    color: #00D4AA;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .hero-stat-num {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .hero-stat-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #555;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  /* Mission */
  .mission {
    padding: 160px 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .mission-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .mission h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .mission p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Features */
  .features {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .features-header {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .features-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 40px 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.2);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.03);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    padding: 200px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-glow {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    padding: 32px 48px;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #888;
  }

  .footer-org {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #444;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .footer-right {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .footer-right a {
    color: #555;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .footer-right a:hover {
    color: #00D4AA;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #444;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #00D4AA;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .hero { padding: 120px 24px 60px; }
    .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px; }
    .hero-stat-divider { display: none; }
    .mission { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .features { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta { padding: 120px 24px; }
    .footer { padding: 24px; }
    .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
